snippet: The distribution of a draft resolution to all United Nations member states is the first practical act in an effort likely to pit the Palestinians against Israel.
abstract: Palestinian official in West Bank says distribution of draft resolution at United Nations is  'first big step' toward vote on enhancing Palestinians’ UN status.
lead_paragraph: The distribution of a draft resolution to all United Nations member states is the first practical act in an effort likely to pit the Palestinians against Israel.

headline.seo: Palestinians Renew Push for Enhanced U.N. Status
headline.main: Palestinians Renew Push for Enhanced U.N. Status
